  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a city sprawling along a coastline at dusk. The cityscape is densely packed with lights, creating a vibrant network across the urban landscape. A large body of water, likely a bay or estuary, separates the city from rolling hills in the distance. The sky is a dramatic canvas of oranges, reds, and deep blues, with streaks of clouds adding texture and depth. The lighting suggests either sunrise or sunset, casting a warm glow over the scene. In the foreground, a dark, silhouetted hillside provides a contrasting base for the luminous city below. The overall impression is one of immense scale and natural beauty combined with urban development.",
